snippet.title: OCTOPATH TRAVELER II | Launch Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
OCTOPATH TRAVELER II will release worldwide on February 24th, 2023 on Nintendo Switch, Steam, PlayStation 5 and PlayStation 4.
More information here: https://www.octopathtraveler2.com

Discover a brand-new entry in the OCTOPATH TRAVELER series, the first installment of which was initially released in 2018 and sold over 3 million copies worldwide. It takes the series’ HD-2D graphics, a fusion of retro pixel art and 3DCG, to even greater heights.

In the faraway realm of Solistia, step into the shoes of eight new travelers, each with their own origins, motivations, and unique skills. 
Some people thrill to glamorous stars of the stage and industry, while others are brought to tears by war, plague, and poverty. 
Explore the land as you see fit, using their unique talents to aid you along your journey. 

Embark on an adventure all your own!

Keep up to date with the latest #OctopathTraveler2 news by following us at:
https://www.twitter.com/SquareEnix
https://www.facebook.com/SquareEnix
https://www.instagram.com/SquareEnix
